	(slime-read-system-name): Use SWANK:LIST-ASDF-SYSTEMS.

	* swank.lisp (list-all-systems-in-central-registry): Use only
	pathname name.

	(list-all-systems-known-to-asdf): New function.

	(list-asdf-systems): New function.

