	* slime.el (sldb-sexp-highlight-mode): Remove bloat.

2006-11-04  Matthias Koeppe  <mkoeppe@mail.math.uni-magdeburg.de>

	Support nested presentations in REPL results, when present.lisp is
	loaded. 
	
